The Claim and Our Verdict
**The claim**: A video claims to show Britain‚Äôs new Prime Minister Rishi Sunak dancing at a party.
**Fact-checking:**
1.  There is no evidence that the man in the viral video is Rishi Sunak. The video was published in July 2019 on Instagram by Wayne Lineker. It actually shows people dancing at a club in Ibiza, Spain. In recent years, Lineker has repeatedly posted the same video on social media to express his stance and attitude towards different social events.
2.  Several media outlets and fact-checking organizations have debunked similar claims, clarifying that the man in the video is not Rishi Sunak but his lookalike. The French news channel France 24 has pointed out that Sunak has a mole on the left side of his face, but the man in the video does not.
3.  According to Sunak‚Äôs official social media accounts, in July 2019, he stayed in the U.K. and attended various events in the country. Therefore, he did not go to Ibiza in Spain, nor he appeared in the viral video.
**Our verdict**: The man dancing in the viral video is not Britain‚Äôs new Prime Minister Rishi Sunak.

Rishi Sunak At Beach Party? No, Viral Video Features UK PM‚Äôs Doppelganger
=========================================================================
Written By 
October 27, 2022
7192
(blob:https://newschecker.in/2ce496c5eb8a85c92c3b8a2bb8391f23)]
### Authors
(blob:https://newschecker.in/3d7e3536fb2191eecfa4af1023c9b129)]
##### 
Vasudha noticed the growing problem of mis/disinformation online after studying New Media at ACJ in Chennai and became interested in separating facts from fiction. She is interested in learning how global issues affect individuals on a micro level. Before joining Newschecker‚Äôs English team, she was working with Latestly.
_(The article was originally published in  by Saurabh Pandey)_
Claim
-----
The newly appointed Prime Minister of the UK, ****, is seen dancing at a beach party.
!(blob:https://newschecker.in/0c419a7e7c4949efea44eb8cd798fc4c)
Screenshot of Facebook post by @ashley.millsdale
Fact
----
We conducted Google reverse image searches on the keyframes of the viral video which led us to a report by , dated January 24, 2022, titled ‚ÄòRaving Rishi living his best life when Boris gets fired‚Äô: Video of **Chancellor‚Äôs doppelg√§nger** throwing shapes in Wayne Lineker‚Äôs Ibiza club sets social media on fire‚Äô
Displaying visuals from the viral video, the report elaborated, ‚ÄúA video of a **Rishi Sunak doppelg√§nger** dancing at Wayne Lineker‚Äôs Ibiza club has set social media alight. The footage shows a man, who has since been dubbed ‚ÄòRaving Rishi‚Äô, cutting shapes at a sunny party¬† surrounded by hundreds of party-goers.‚Äù
!(blob:https://newschecker.in/6924d057e0400429f0cc70a1e266db91)
Screengrab from Daily Mail website
It added, ‚ÄúIt is unclear when the video was taken or the identity of **Mr Sunak‚Äôs lookalike**, but the footage appears to have been taken at Mr Lineker‚Äôs O Beach Ibiza club on the Spanish party island.‚Äù
The video clip was reportedly posted on Wayne Lineker‚Äôs Instagram page ‚Äì the owner of the beach club in Ibiza.
A report by , dated January 24, 2022, corroborated with the details of the Daily Mail article,...[Content truncated]
